x4freetext: -The fission cross sections of U-233, U-234, U-236,
U-238, Np-237, Pu-239 and Pu-241 relative to that of
U-235 for neutrons in the energy range 1-14 MeV-
15 micro-amp of 2-3 MeV particles incident on
a gas cell through 0.003 mm thick molybdenum
.Corrections of up to 4 percent applied to observed
fission rates to determine total fission rate.
.Error in relative values due to corrections, counting
statistics and uncertainties in the mass of fissile
material gives standard deviation of 2 percent.
.Monitor uncertainty of about 3 percent leads to final
